	<h1 class="title">外界干扰不一定会降低工作效率，却会让你觉得不幸福</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/451727/small/451727.jpg?1454344526" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">华凤仪 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-27 07:05:51 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/26032/medium/26032.jpg?1461651987" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="26032" data-title="《外界干扰不一定会降低工作效率，却会让你觉得不幸福》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/26032/medium/26032.jpg?1461651987" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/26032.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
